d by running enemies over, power slides, handbrake turns, completing Road Races, jumping through Stunt Rings and collecting Renegade Driving Orbs; Explosives, which is obviously increased by using explosives, both Launchers and thrown Grenades; and last but not least: Strength, which is increased by using hand-to-hand attacks, throwing objects, beating people with those objects, or using the moves you unlock as your Strength increases, such as the Charge or Ground Slam.", :release_date => "2010-07-06", :title => "Crackdown 2", :developer => "Ruffian Games", :publisher => "Microsoft Games Studio", :coverart_remote_url => 'http://thegamesdb.net/banners/boxart/original/front/12062-1.jpg')
